    on right: 18 19
    on left : 20
  io_redirect (32)
    on right: 22 23 26 27
    on left : 30 31
  io_file (33)
    on right: 30 31
    on left : 32 33 34 35 36
  filename (34)
    on right: 32 33 34 35 36
    on left : 37

**Terminals, with rules where they appear

  $end (0) 
  error (1) 
  WORD (2) 20 21 28 29 37
  ASSIGNMENT_WORD (3) 24 25
  IO_NUMBER (4) 31
  NEWLINE (5) 40 41
  AND_IF (6) 10
  OR_IF (7) 11
  DGREAT (8) 34
  LESSGREAT (9) 35
  CLOBBER (10) 36
  "<" (11) 32
  ">" (12) 33
  "&" (13) 38
  ";" (14) 39

--------- State ---------

state 0


  NEWLINE       shift, and go to state 3
  $default      reduce using rule 43 (linebreak)

  program       go to state 1
  linebreak     go to state 2
  newline_list  go to state 4

state 1


  $end          shift, and go to state 5


